window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Miles “Shrug” Lindstrom has endured the first few days of his new monster-infested world.</b></p> <p>He has become the Champion of a god, and managed to become one of the most powerful survivors in his area.</p> <p>However, a new quest to kill a giant—a boss monster—will be difficult if not impossible to accomplish by himself. Gathering more power for himself is a safe bet towards all of his goals, and might be easier now that he has a class. But if this new world is anything, it’s uncertain.</p> <p>Join Miles as he continues to navigate a newly post-apocalypse world full of monsters, magic, and people demonstrating the very best, and very worst that humanity has to offer.</p> <p>Will he accept the expectations that other survivors have for him? Will he reject them? Or will he find his own path?</p> <p><b>Book 2 in the next LitRPG Apocalypse Series from bestseller Blaise Corvin, author of </b><b><i>Delvers LLC</i></b><b> and </b><b><i>Apocalypse Cultivation</i></b><b>. Sometimes, being the chosen one isn’t all it’s cracked up to be.</b></p>"; 
